title: No.25 Augustana Soccer defeated by No. 12 Minnesota State 2-1 (Augustana Vikings Athletics)
text: ( Source : Augustana Vikings Athletics ) SIOUX FALLS, S.D. - No.25 Augustana soccer had its 11 game unbeaten streak snapped with a 2-1 defeat to No. 12 Minnesota State on Sunday at Morstad Field . The loss dropped the Vikings record to 11-2-1,
